'''Applied Unified Communications''' is the application of [[unified communications]] ([[SMS]], [[e-mail]], [[VoIP]], Letters, [[Interactive voice response|IVR]]) to solve business problems by helping enterprises to increase [[Profit (economics)|profitability]] and operational efficiencies using targeted and personalised [[communication]]s with their [[customer]]s.

